ne change needed). Honest: only tagged checks produce SCuBA rows; 23 baseline policies + all Power BI are not yet assessed (feeds a future net-new-check release). Tag-only: no check logic/scoring/count changes (473 checks, 46 public functions). Test verify-scuba-crosswalk.ps1 (12/12). See CHANGELOG.md for v2.22.0 and earlier.'
